<p><a href="#sdfootnote8anc" name="sdfootnote8sym">8</a> Barbara Johnson, <em>Bringing Out D.A. Miller</em>, „Narrative” 2002, nr 1, s. 3–8.</p>
<p><a href="#sdfootnote9anc" name="sdfootnote9sym">9</a> Zob. Leo Bersani, Adam Phillips, <em>Intimacies,</em> University of Chicago Press, Chicago 2008; oraz Tim Dean, <em>Unlimited Intimacy. Reflections on the Subculture of Barebacking</em>, University of Chicago Press, Chicago 2009.</p>
